  "title": "Medical Billing & Insurance Executive - Central [GC]",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Assist patients by providing information on local and overseas insurance panels, MediShield coverage, claim timelines, and other related enquiries</p></li><li><p>Manage accurate and timely insurance claims processing, including verification, billing, collections, payment posting, accounts receivable, and coordination with clinical and corporate teams</p></li><li><p>Adhere to established procedures and ensure compliance with updated or new MOH regulations and implementation guidelines</p></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Degree or Diploma in Business Studies or a related discipline</p></li><li><p>Minimum 3 years of relevant experience in the healthcare industry</p></li></ul><p><br /></p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p><p><br /></p><p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
